question: Siu-tshùn tshuā-ui-ê sóo-tsāi, tshiánn-tuānn-suí tsū-tíng tshin-lâng tshut-laínn tuì nn̄g-ê bô-kāng-ê tshut-gōo tūinn tūinn tuì uī-tsiúê kóo-tsiong.
Sri Lanka chiah ê kok-chhiú tan-chhiú, siáⁿ-choán ê pâi-chu̍t ê àn-suànn-sò͘ sī chá-seng? (What is the average number of runs scored in partnerships where Sri Lanka was the batting team?)
Kumar Sangakkara bē sī-koh tit-tâi ê ha̍p-chok, lóng chòe-lióng chē sió-siâⁿ kóe?

Chiu-liâm ê ha̍p-chok pn̄g-sò͘ ê choân-thé tûng-hiòng sī siáⁿ-chóa-khoán, tùi siāng chá ê kì-lo̍k kàu siāng boé ê kì-lo̍k? Chit ê chu-liāu ū chāi-chāiⁿ kóng-bêng siāng-koân ê ha̍p-chok lóng bat tit-tio̍h koh-khah chē ê pn̄g bô?
answer: Chit ê chu-liāu sī lia̍t chhut kòe si̍p-tang-la̍k ê sî-chūn, siāng-koân ê ha̍p-chok ê pn̄g-sò͘ ū chi̍t ê choân-thé siōng-hiòng. Siāng chá ê 451 hām 446 ê pn̄g, lóng sī 1934 hām 1957/58 nî ê chu-liāu. Tān-sī, siāng-koân ê nn̄g ê pn̄g, 624 hām 576 pn̄g, lóng sī chāi-chāiⁿ 2006 hām 1997 nî tit-tio̍h ê. Sui-bóng ū chi̍t-kóa tiau-seng, siāng-koân ê pn̄g-sò͘ lóng sī ùi chāi-chāiⁿ ê sî-tāi. Chit-ê tiāⁿ-tiāⁿ sī kóng-bêng siāng-koân ê ha̍p-chok lóng bat tit-tio̍h koh-khah chē ê pn̄g ê.

question: Liāu sū-kiû 2 ūi koat-tó͘ khah koân 440 jiám ê só͘-chāi ê miâ-jī.
Tae chit ge phiau chheh lai ê ha̍p-chok, ū to-siâu phiah sī Sri Lanka ê tai-pa̍t tūi só͘ siâⁿ ê? Kiám-chiap tio̍h chi̍t-ê sió-sò͘.

Jiak-sī kin-kú 1990 niâ chìn-chá ê season ê ha̍p-chok lóng hō͘ chha̍h tńg, chiūⁿ chit-ê lia̍t-toa̍t siōng, tē 3 hō kià-liâu ê sîn-thâu ê pêng-kin hō͘-sò͘ ē sī chi̍t ê sin ê sò͘-ba̍k? Ū * ê hō͘-sò͘ ài chò phó͘-thong ê sò͘-ba̍k lâi phóe, chiū ē chò siāng-kūn ê chéng-sò͘.
Tī chit-ê su-liệu-khò͘ lāi-bīn, ū chin chheng-chhó ê koan-liân, chí-chā tē 2 bāng ê ha̍p-chok lóng koh-ì-tiāⁿ tit chhē khah chē hun chhiáⁿ tē 3 tē 4 bāng ê ha̍p-chok?
answer: Bōe, tī chit-ê su-liệu-khò͘ lāi-bīn bô chin chheng-chhó ê koan-liân, lâi chí-chā tē gōa bāng sī koh-ì-tiāⁿ tit chhē khah chē hun. Tē 3 bāng ê ha̍p-chok ê pêng-kin hun (492.75 hun) pí tē 2 bāng ê ha̍p-chok (477.75 hun) khah koân chi̍t-ē. Koh chi̍t-ê, siōng koân ê 624 hun ê ha̍p-chok sī tē 3 bāng tit--ê, chit siâⁿ tò-tńg chiah ū liáu-kái tē gōa bāng ê ha̍p-chok lóng sī siōng koân ê khò͘-siā.

question: Koh-tuí ê sńg-tiám hō͘ jī-bīn, só͘-chāi tùi pa̍t-ê tī lia̍t-toaⁿ téng-bīn lâi kóng, sī siáⁿ-mih hō͘ i sī chi̍t ê te̍k-pia̍t tōa ê sò͘-ba̍t, chiàⁿ-bô͘i koh-tuí teh kóng sī siáⁿ-mih?
answer: 624 sńg-tiám ê tīn-tūi, sī Mahela Jayawardene hām Kumar Sangakkara, sī chi̍t ê chin te̍k-pia̍t tōa ê sò͘-ba̍t. Chú-iàu ê tiám-sò͘ sī tī 429 kàu 467 sńg-tiám tiong-kan. 624 sńg-tiám ê tīn-tūi sī 48 sńg-tiám khah chē tùi tē-2 chē ê tīn-tūi (576), chiàⁿ-bô͘i sī 157 sńg-tiám khah chē tùi tē-3 chē ê tīn-tūi (467), hō͘ i tī chi̍t ê tūi lāi-bīn to̍h-ài kóng sī chin te̍k-pia̍t ê.

question: Chiah-ê 'Season' chiam-sû, iōng nn̄g khoán bô-kâng ê hong-sek lâi piáu-sī liân-hūn. Chit nn̄g khoán hong-sek sī siáⁿ-mih, koh siáⁿ-khoán sī khah tiāⁿ chhut-hiān tī chiah-ê phiau-chû-lâng lāi?
answer: Chit nn̄g khoán hong-sek sī chi̍t-ê liân-hūn (YYYY) chhiūⁿ '2006', kap chi̍t-ê hun-khui ê liân-hūn piáu-sī chi̍t-ê bao-koat nn̄g-ê nî-tō͘ ê kí-liâu (YYYY/YY) chhiūⁿ '1990/91'. Chi̍t-ê liân-hūn (YYYY) hong-sek khah phó͘-thong, chhut-hiān 5 pái, kap hun-khui ê liân-hūn hong-sek ê 4 pái.

question: Oa-tiⁿ hō͘ India phah-chhut siōng koân ê ha̍p-chok phah-sǹg ê sī siáng?
